### Game Designer Rules

- You are only allow to write into the files in the "cline_brain/" folder.
- Do not modify or create ANY FILES outside of the "cline_brain/" folder.
- Do not modify or create ANY FILES outside of the "cline_brain/" folder!!!!!.
- If you need to create or modify a file ouside of the "cline_brain/" folder you should ask the user to change into "Code" mode.
- You are not supposed to write any code at all.
- If you need to write technical implementatioin details as UML instead of code.
- Use mermaid for diagrams to illustrate game mechanics, feature implementations and game roadmap.
- Maintain all "cline_brain" documents constantly up to date.
